ent\", \"from\": 246, \"to\": 262}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 266, \"to\": 271}, {\"ngram\": \"the community\", \"from\": 276, \"to\": 289}, {\"ngram\": \"their Island fishermen\", \"from\": 305, \"to\": 327}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The idea is to celebrate the working waterfront and the commercial fishermen and give people a chance to meet the fishermen who harvest their seafood because oftentimes you just see the boat coming in or going out, but you do not have a chance to see the face behind your dinner,\\\" said Shelley Edmundson, executive director of the preservation trust.\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 681, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 617, \"end\": 624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_South_Park_families\", \"score\": 0.9922594607189298, \"rank\": 0.007800922620199822, \"text\": \"Shelley\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_South_Park_families\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_South_Park_families\"}, {\"begin\": 625, \"end\": 634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Helen_Edmundson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.870195562216004e-15, \"text\": \"Edmundson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Helen_Edmundson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Helen_Edmundson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The idea\", \"from\": 331, \"to\": 339}, {\"ngram\": \"the working waterfront\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 378}, {\"ngram\": \"the commercial fishermen\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 407}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 417, \"to\": 423}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 432}, {\"ngram\": \"the fishermen\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 454}, {\"ngram\": \"their seafood\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 480}, {\"ngram\": \"the boat\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 521}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 566, \"to\": 574}, {\"ngram\": \"the face\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 590}, {\"ngram\": \"your dinner\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 609}, {\"ngram\": \"executive director\", \"from\": 636, \"to\": 654}, {\"ngram\": \"the preservation trust\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 680}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Around 20 commercial fishing vessels pulled up to the docks stern in.\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 752, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Around 20 commercial fishing vessels\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 719}, {\"ngram\": \"the docks\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 742}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They were supposed to be in by 2 pm but most of them were in by noon, Edmundson said, alluding to an eagerness amongst participants.\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 885, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 823, \"end\": 832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Helen_Edmundson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.870195562216004e-15, \"text\": \"Edmundson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Helen_Edmundson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Helen_Edmundson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"2 pm\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 788}, {\"ngram\": \"noon\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 821}, {\"ngram\": \"an eagerness\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 863}, {\"ngram\": \"participants\", \"from\": 872, \"to\": 884}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They had more boats actually than they'd anticipated, both from the Island and mainland.\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 974, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more boats\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 905}, {\"ngram\": \"the Island\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 960}, {\"ngram\": \"mainland\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 973}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's always a really good turnout,\\\" Edmundson added.\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 1029, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1013, \"end\": 1022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Helen_Edmundson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.870195562216004e-15, \"text\": \"Edmundson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Helen_Edmundson\", \"dbpedi