, \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2331}, {\"ngram\": \"the waters\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2354}, {\"ngram\": \"the commonwealth\", \"from\": 2358, \"to\": 2374}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sergeant Ian Haskins focuses mostly on the Southeast coast, but because he is federally deputized, he also patrols federal waters.\", \"from\": 2376, \"to\": 2506, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2376, \"end\": 2384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sergeant\", \"score\": 0.9999893297864146, \"rank\": 1.0663669025620225e-05, \"text\": \"Sergeant\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sergeant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sergeant\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Southeast coast\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2434}, {\"ngram\": \"federal waters\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2505}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Haskins uses the vessel for presence and response to boat safety as well as commercial and recreational fishing practices.\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2629, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Haskins\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2514}, {\"ngram\": \"the vessel\", \"from\": 2520, \"to\": 2530}, {\"ngram\": \"presence\", \"from\": 2535, \"to\": 2543}, {\"ngram\": \"response\", \"from\": 2548, \"to\": 2556}, {\"ngram\": \"boat safety\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2571}, {\"ngram\": \"commercial and recreational fishing practices\", \"from\": 2583, \"to\": 2628}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On board was a remote-controlled submersible that the police use for recovering fatalities and ensuring compliance of fishing gear.\", \"from\": 2631, \"to\": 2762, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"board\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2639}, {\"ngram\": \"a remote-controlled submersible\", \"from\": 2644, \"to\": 2675}, {\"ngram\": \"the police\", \"from\": 2681, \"to\": 2691}, {\"ngram\": \"fatalities\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2721}, {\"ngram\": \"compliance\", \"from\": 2735, \"to\": 2745}, {\"ngram\": \"fishing gear\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2761}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Around 5 pm, crowds gathered at the beach for a Coast Guard helicopter rescue demonstration.\", \"from\": 2764, \"to\": 2856, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2812, \"end\": 2823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Coast_Guard\", \"score\": 0.999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.215493931132104e-12, \"text\": \"Coast Guard\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Coast_Guard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Coast_Guard\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"crowds\", \"from\": 2777, \"to\": 2783}, {\"ngram\": \"the beach\", \"from\": 2796, \"to\": 2805}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Justin Harris, chief engineering officer at the Coast Guard's Chilmark base, described the demonstration to Times' reporters from the beach.\", \"from\": 2857, \"to\": 2997, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2905, \"end\": 2916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Coast_Guard\", \"score\": 0.999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.215493931132104e-12, \"text\": \"Coast Guard\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Coast_Guard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Coast_Guard\"}, {\"begin\": 2919, \"end\": 2927, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicksgrove_Quarry\", \"score\": 0.9999990571845853, \"rank\": 9.428162672808161e-07, \"text\": \"Chilmark\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicksgrove_Quarry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicksgrove_Quarry\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Justin Harris\", \"from\": 2857, \"to\": 2870}, {\"ngram\": \"chief engineering officer\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 2897}, {\"ngram\": \"the demonstration\", \"from\": 2944, \"to\": 2961}, {\"ngram\": \"Times' reporters\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 2981}, {\"ngram\": \"the beach\", \"from\": 2987, \"to\": 2996}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The demonstrators mocked both a basket rescue and a direct rescue, Harris said.\", \"from\": 2998, \"to\": 3077, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The demonstrators\", \"from\": 2998, \"to\": 3015}, {\"ngram\": \"both a basket rescue\", \"from\": 3023, \"to\": 3043}, {\"ngram\": \"a direct rescue\", \"from\": 3048, \"to\": 3063}, {\"ngram\": \"Harris\", \"from\": 3065, \"to\": 3071}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These are water rescues, he said, but they can be done on boats too.\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3147, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"water rescues\", \"from\": 3089, \"to\": 3102}, {\"ngram\": \"boats\", \"from\": 3137, \"to\": 3142}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Musical groups Rose Guerin, Rose Colored Glasses, the Philly Project, and Dock Dance Band played off the deck of the F/V Martha Elizabeth, captained by lobster and conch commercial fisherman Wes Brighton, as green crab races, a net-mending competition, and a fish-filleting demonstration occurred in between the buildings.\", \"from\": 3149, \"to\": 3471, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3164, \"end\": 3168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose\", \"score\": 0.8903262632659739, \"rank\": 0.12316212823277509, \"text\": \"Rose\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose\"}, {\"begin\": 3169, \"end\": 3175, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 5.06624078282096e-13, \"text\": \"Guerin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\"}, {\"begin\": 3177, \"end\": 3197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Colored_Glasses_(Kelly_Rowland_song)\", \"score\": 0.8329048821309396, \"rank\": 0.15123456790117798, \"text\": \"Rose Colored Glasses\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Colored_Glasses_(Kelly_Ro